<p style=3D"margin: 16px 0;">I just want to put it out there that a really =
interesting=C2=A0securities fraud lawsuit against Bed Bath &amp; Beyond Inc=
.=C2=A0is, like, two weeks away. <a href=3D"https://link.mail.bloombergbusi=
ness.com/click/31219425.261443/aHR0cHM6Ly93d3cuYmxvb21iZXJnLmNvbS9uZXdzL2Fy=
dGljbGVzLzIwMjMtMDQtMTkvYmVkLWJhdGgtYmV5b25kLXJldml2ZXMtYmFua3J1cHRjeS1wcmV=
wYXJhdGlvbnMtYXMtc3RvY2stZmFsbHM_Y21waWQ9QkJEMDQxOTIzX01PTkVZU1RVRkYmdXRtX2=
1lZGl1bT1lbWFpbCZ1dG1fc291cmNlPW5ld3NsZXR0ZXImdXRtX3Rlcm09MjMwNDE5JnV0bV9jY=
W1wYWlnbj1tb25leXN0dWZm/607f07ceef4b8524a319a23cB979fda52" itemprop=3D"Stor=
yLink" itemscope=3D"itemscope" target=3D"_blank" style=3D"color: #000000; t=
ext-decoration: none !important; border-bottom-width: 1px; border-bottom-co=
lor: #000000; border-bottom-style: solid; background-color: #ccc;">  Bloomb=
erg News reports</a>:</p>
<blockquote>
<p style=3D"margin: 16px 0;">Bed Bath &amp; Beyond Inc.=C2=A0is once again =
laying the groundwork for a bankruptcy filing as its last-ditch efforts to =
raise cash come up short.=C2=A0</p>
<p style=3D"margin: 16px 0;">The retailer is holding talks with advisers an=
d lenders ahead of a Chapter 11 filing that could come in the next few week=
s, according to people with knowledge of the conversations, who asked not t=
o be named discussing private plans. Bed Bath &amp; Beyond is also looking =
at financing options to help fund itself during bankruptcy, the people adde=
d.=C2=A0</p>
<p style=3D"margin: 16px 0;">The filing could come before an April 26 deadl=
ine by which the company=C2=A0sought=C2=A0to raise another $300 million fro=
m equity investors, the people said, adding that a decision isn=E2=80=99t f=
inal and plans could change.=C2=A0</p>
<p style=3D"margin: 16px 0;">Bed Bath &amp; Beyond has shocked investors be=
fore: earlier this year, the company=C2=A0staved off=C2=A0a bankruptcy fili=
ng after raising $360 million from a hedge fund investor that bought shares=
 at a discount. ...</p>
<p style=3D"margin: 16px 0;">Even as the retailer prepares for bankruptcy, =
shares staged another rally in a move reminiscent of meme-stock mania two y=
ears ago, where wild swings in stocks became commonplace. Bed Bath &amp; Be=
yond spiked 41% in the first 40 minutes of trading on Wednesday, bringing t=
he stock price to nearly 49 cents, more than double its closing price last =
week.</p>
</blockquote>
<p style=3D"margin: 16px 0;">Bed Bath &amp; Beyond has been <a href=3D"http=
s://link.mail.bloombergbusiness.com/click/31219425.261443/aHR0cHM6Ly93d3cuY=
mxvb21iZXJnLmNvbS9vcGluaW9uL2FydGljbGVzLzIwMjMtMDMtMzAvYmVkLWJhdGgtYmV5b25k=
LWhhcy1tb3JlLXN0b2NrLXRvLXNlbGw_Y21waWQ9QkJEMDQxOTIzX01PTkVZU1RVRkYmdXRtX21=
lZGl1bT1lbWFpbCZ1dG1fc291cmNlPW5ld3NsZXR0ZXImdXRtX3Rlcm09MjMwNDE5JnV0bV9jYW=
1wYWlnbj1tb25leXN0dWZm/607f07ceef4b8524a319a23cBbd9ba10b" itemprop=3D"Story=
Link" itemscope=3D"itemscope" target=3D"_blank" style=3D"color: #000000; te=
xt-decoration: none !important; border-bottom-width: 1px; border-bottom-col=
or: #000000; border-bottom-style: solid; background-color: #ccc;">  poundin=
g out</a> tens of millions of dollars of stock to retail investors in at-th=
e-market stock offerings <a href=3D"https://link.mail.bloombergbusiness.com=
/click/31219425.261443/aHR0cHM6Ly93d3cuYmxvb21iZXJnLmNvbS9vcGluaW9uL2FydGlj=
bGVzLzIwMjMtMDQtMTIvc3BhYy1waXBlcy1zb21ldGltZXMtbGVhaz9jbXBpZD1CQkQwNDE5MjN=
fTU9ORVlTVFVGRiZ1dG1fbWVkaXVtPWVtYWlsJnV0bV9zb3VyY2U9bmV3c2xldHRlciZ1dG1fdG=
VybT0yMzA0MTkmdXRtX2NhbXBhaWduPW1vbmV5c3R1ZmY/607f07ceef4b8524a319a23cB32b5=
0e30" itemprop=3D"StoryLink" itemscope=3D"itemscope" target=3D"_blank" styl=
e=3D"color: #000000; text-decoration: none !important; border-bottom-width:=
 1px; border-bottom-color: #000000; border-bottom-style: solid; background-=
color: #ccc;">  as all this has been going on</a>; for all I know it has be=
en selling stock into=C2=A0<em>today=E2=80=99s=C2=A0</em>rally. Why not? In=
 all of its public disclosure, Bed Bath has been reasonably clear about the=
 risks that investors face, with the main one being that the company is pro=
bably going to go bankrupt with no recovery for the equity. =E2=80=9CWe exp=
ect that we will likely file for bankruptcy protection notwithstanding the =
sale of common stock pursuant to the Purchase Agreement,=E2=80=9D <a href=
=3D"https://link.mail.bloombergbusiness.com/click/31219425.261443/aHR0cHM6L=
y93d3cuc2VjLmdvdi9peD9kb2M9L0FyY2hpdmVzL2VkZ2FyL2RhdGEvODg2MTU4LzAwMDExOTMx=
MjUyMzA5Nzk4Mi9kNDk2NTQ5ZHMxLmh0bQ/607f07ceef4b8524a319a23cB73a810e1" itemp=
rop=3D"StoryLink" itemscope=3D"itemscope" target=3D"_blank" style=3D"color:=
 #000000; text-decoration: none !important; border-bottom-width: 1px; borde=
r-bottom-color: #000000; border-bottom-style: solid; background-color: #ccc=
;"> Bed Bath said</a> in the risk factors to its stock offering prospectus =
last week. And now the stock has gone=C2=A0<em>up</em>=C2=A0today on report=
s that=C2=A0bankruptcy is closer.</p>
<p style=3D"margin: 16px 0;">Somebody is buying Bed Bath stock today at $0.=
46,=C2=A0<em>possibly from the company itself</em>,<a class=3D"footnote-ind=
