</a> and if that stock becomes worthless in a week because of a bankruptcy =
filing that person is going to sue. Though of course the stock will probabl=
y rally even more if the company actually files. (Will the company keep sel=
ling stock after it files? <a href=3D"https://link.mail.bloombergbusiness.c=
om/click/31219425.261443/aHR0cHM6Ly93d3cuYmxvb21iZXJnLmNvbS9vcGluaW9uL2FydG=
